---
import MainLayout from "../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="OmniConverter - 全能电子书转换工具"
  description="以闪电般的速度在 PDF、EPUB、FB2、RTF、TXT、CHM、MOBI、AZW 和 DJVU 之间转换您的文档。您的完整电子书转换解决方案。"
>
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100 dark:from-primary-900 dark:to-primary-800">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            OmniConverter
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-200 mb-8">
            您的首选电子书转换工具，无缝转换多种格式的文档。
            无论是学术论文还是小说，OmniConverter 都能让您的阅读体验在不同格式之间保持连贯。
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
            <a
              href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6499086601?mt=8"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-200"
            >
              在 Mac App Store 下载
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <img
            src="/screenshots/omniconverter-hero.png"
            alt="OmniConverter 界面"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Features Section -->
    <section class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-primary-900 dark:text-white mb-16">
        强大功能，无缝转换
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Speed & Efficiency -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">闪电般快速转换</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            先进的多线程技术确保您的文件以闪电般的速度转换。支持批量处理多个文件。
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- User Interface -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">直观界面</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            简洁、简单的界面，一键操作。无需复杂设置即可获得完美结果。
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Format Support -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">广泛的格式支持</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            支持所有主要电子书格式，包括 PDF、EPUB、FB2、RTF、TXT、CHM、MOBI、AZW 和 DJVU。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Format Support Details -->
    <section class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
          全面的格式支持
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">输入格式</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mt-1 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">CHM、FB2、RTF、HTML、MHTML</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mt-1 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">MOBI、AZW（Kindle 格式）</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mt-1 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">EPUB、PDF、TXT</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mt-1 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">DJVU、WPD</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">输出格式</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mt-1 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">PDF、EPUB、HTML</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mt-1 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">TXT（UTF-8 编码）</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Additional Features -->
    <section class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
          为什么选择 OmniConverter？
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">持续改进</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              定期更新以修复问题、添加新功能并提升用户体验。您的反馈推动着我们的发展。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">隐私与安全</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              我们认真对待您的隐私。OmniConverter 不会收集或分享您的个人信息或文档内容。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">客户支持</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              我们的客户服务团队随时准备用您的语言为您提供帮助。我们随时解答任何问题或提供支持。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-20">
      <div class="bg-primary-600 rounded-2xl p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          准备好转换您的文档了吗？
        </h2>
        <p class="text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          立即下载 OmniConverter，体验在所有您喜爱的格式之间无缝转换文档。
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6499086601?mt=8"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary-600 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-200"
        >
          在 Mac App Store 下载
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .bg-grid-pattern {
    background-image: linear-gradient(
        to right,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 1px,
        transparent 1px
      ),
      linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 20px 20px;
  }
</style>
